title: Increase alUSD debt ceiling
body:
A few days ago, alUSD reached its debt cap. 
To meet the communities demand, we are proposing to raise this cap.

The options are:
1. Do nothing
2. Increase debt ceiling by 10% (10m alUSD)
3. Increase debt ceiling by 15% (15m alUSD)
4. Increase debt ceiling by 20% (20m alUSD)

Arguments for raising the debt cap:
- There is demand from the users and community to increase the debt cap
- alUSD is currently on peg, with 1 alUSD = 0.999 DAI
- More deposits increases system revenue

Arguments against raising the debt cap:
- More deposits in the Alchemix Vault would lower the yield boost from the Transmuter
- Extra alUSD supply could affect the peg
